===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[Arabian]] [[peninsula|Peninsula]]''' (the)
# A [[peninsula]] in the [[w:Middle East|Middle East]], bordered on by [[w:Iraq|Iraq]] and [[w:Jordan|Jordan]] to the north, the [[w:Persian Gulf|Persian Gulf]] to the northeast, the [[w:Red Sea|Red Sea]] to the southwest and the [[w:Indian Ocean|Indian Ocean]] to the southeast. It consists mainly of [[w:Saudi Arabia|Saudi Arabia]].

